These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, turkish, malaysian
1. the malaysian is on the left of the turkish##1
2. the malaysian is between the australian and the turkish##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |  2   |    3     |
| Nationality   | australian | malaysian | turkish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-2::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: crime, adventure, epic
1. the person watching crime movies is between the person watching adventure movies and the person watching epic movies##2
2. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | crime | adventure |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-3::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, hip-hop, rock
1. the fan of hip-hop is between the fan of disco and the fan of rock##2
2. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |  2   |    3    |
| Music-Genre   | rock | hip-hop | disco |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-4::.
3 different pets are kept: cat, fish, frog
1. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
2. the owner of the frog is between the owner of the fish and the owner of the cat##2

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2   |     3      |
| Pet   | cat | frog | fish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-5::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, sprite, water
1. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person drinking water and the person drinking sprite##2
2. the person drinking water is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |  2   |  3   |
| Beverage   | sprite | soy-milk | water |

 #################################

 
